We got you bro(w)!⁣⁣
.⁣⁣
As the frame of your face, #eyebrows add personality and fierceness – but hey, if they’re too bold, you could go from fierce to downright scary, isn’t it?⁣⁣
.⁣⁣
So, for today’s #POPxoMakeup101 lesson, @iamhimanikhatri is going to share with you how to define your brows - fill and conceal - to make them look clean and dramatic! So, let’s start:⁣⁣
.⁣⁣
✨ Before you head on to filling in your brows, take an angled brow brush (also known as a slanted liner brush) and use it to brush your brows upwards⁣⁣
✨ Pick a colour that is a shade or two lighter than the natural colour of your brows and start by first outlining your brows using a setting powder⁣⁣
✨ Fine-tune your product so that you don't over-do it by accident⁣⁣
✨ As you work on your brows to achieve the perfect shape of eyebrows, make sure that you are making small strokes that give out an appearance of your natural hair⁣⁣
#ProTip: You don't want to overextend the tail end of your eyebrow, it can draw your face down⁣⁣
✨ Brush through brows again with a spoolie to blend out the colour and soften any harsh lines and conceal your brows to make them pop⁣⁣
.⁣⁣
Tag a friend whose #brows speak louder than words!⁣⁣
.⁣⁣
#EyebrowTutorial #Eyebrows #MakeupTutorial #Makeup101

As we continue to wear masks every time we step out, there is no reason why we still can't look our best! Searching for a quick #makeup routine to lift up your mood? Well, we at POPxo have got you covered.⁣
.⁣
So, in today's episode of #POPxoMakeupMasterclass, our #beauty star Himani (@iamhimanikhatri) creates a quicky and easy, everyday makeup that you can do at home:⁣
.⁣
✨ Start by priming your face. Himani used @maccosmeticsindia Prep and Prime Skin Base Visage - Rs. 2750⁣
✨ Apply #foundation and blend it out. Himani used @wetnwildindia Photo Focus Foundation - Rs. 599⁣
✨ Set the under eye area with loose powder. Himani used @makeuprevolutionindia Luxury Powder - Rs. 850⁣
✨ Use a #lipstick to add color to your cheeks. Himani used @nyxcosmetics_in Suede Matte Lipstick (Brunch Me) - Rs.750⁣
✨ Add the same color to your eyelids and lips.⁣
✨ Tightline your the upper lash line with kajal. Himani used @plumgoodness Kohl Kajal - Rs. 425⁣
✨ Add a coat of #mascara. Himani used @maybelline Colossal Mascara - Rs. 405⁣
✨ Brush off any excess powder from the under eye area.⁣
✨ Set your brows with a tinted brow gel. Himani used @nyxcosmetics_in Tinted Brow Mascara - Rs. 600⁣
Voila! You're all set!⁣
.⁣
Tag someone and share this #tutorial!⁣
.⁣
#makeuptutorial #makeupinspo #easymakeup #everydaymakeuplook #makeup
